name: Mr. Coconut

reviews.text:
No seating or trash cans nearby.  Taste is the same as others‚Ä¶ delicious coconut shake!
Located towards entrance 1 side of the mrt

I always go parkway parade outlet, just realised got new outlet in the marine parade mrt.. shop not so visible. Only saw it when I was going ticketing office for enquiries last 2 weeks.

Today i came again bought few cups on my way home share with my family's, feel different very warm welcoming from the little training girl.
She actually remember me and was very friendly chat with me asking how am I, had I taken my lunch, she alone yet was fast too from taking orders and serving and can handle another walking quickly answers their enquiries.  Alone yet can cope well with everything, and still not forget providing good customer services. I was very impressed üëè  by her attitude and services that's why I decided give her an review.

As I been parkway parade so many times, they don't even as friendly or remember me as return customer by giving me warm welcome.
Mustini is a very kind and helpful staff and she knows all her responsibilities and knowledge of her work to the customers
thank you Soh for the great service and patience as i was choosing my drink !
Great place to get a nice chilled coconut drink as you exit the MRT station towards Roxy Square exit.

vicinity: 101 Marine Parade Road, B1-03 MRT Station
